<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ar" dir="rtl">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>إشعار ناقل — أكمل مشاويرك</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Tajawal:wght@300;400;500;700;800;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
  <style>
    :root {
      /* Brand — new green */
      --brand:        #34CC99;
      --brand-600:    #25b082;
      --brand-700:    #1b8f69;
      --brand-800:    #14734f;
      --brand-ink:    #062e20;

      /* Surfaces */
      --bg:           #f4faf7;
      --bg-2:         #eaf5ef;
      --card:         #ffffff;
      --border:       #e2ede7;
      --border-strong:#cfe3d8;

      /* Text */
      --ink:          #0c1c13;
      --ink-2:        #2a3b32;
      --muted:        #647a70;
      --muted-2:      #8ea097;

      /* Accents */
      --gold:         #d6a024;
      --gold-soft:    #fff6df;

      /* Shadows */
      --shadow-sm:    0 1px 2px rgba(6,46,32,.06), 0 1px 1px rgba(6,46,32,.04);
      --shadow-md:    0 6px 20px rgba(6,46,32,.08), 0 2px 6px rgba(6,46,32,.05);
      --shadow-lg:    0 24px 60px rgba(6,46,32,.22), 0 8px 20px rgba(6,46,32,.12);

      /* Radii */
      --r-sm: 10px;
      --r-md: 14px;
      --r-lg: 20px;
      --r-xl: 28px;
    }

    * , *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    html, body { height: 100%; }

    body {
      font-family: 'Tajawal', system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--ink);
      min-height: 100vh;
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
      -moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale;
      font-feature-settings: "kern", "liga", "calt";
      line-height: 1.55;
      padding-bottom: 48px;
      position: relative;
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    /* Subtle ambient backdrop */
    body::before {
      content: '';
      position: fixed; inset: 0;
      background:
        radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 40% at 85% -5%,  rgba(52,204,153,.10) 0%, transparent 60%),
        radial-gradient(ellipse 50% 35% at 10% 105%, rgba(52,204,153,.07) 0%, transparent 60%);
      pointer-events: none;
      z-index: 0;
    }

    .page {
      max-width: 720px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 32px 22px 0;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    /* ============ TOP BAR ============ */
    .topbar {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      padding: 4px 2px;
    }
    .brand-lockup {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
    }
    .brand-mark {
      width: 42px; height: 42px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--brand) 0%, var(--brand-700) 100%);
      display: grid; place-items: center;
      color: #fff;
      font-size: 18px;
      box-shadow: 0 6px 16px rgba(52,204,153,.35), inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,.25);
    }
    .brand-text .bt-name {
      font-size: 17px;
      font-weight: 900;
      color: var(--brand-ink);
      letter-spacing: -.3px;
      line-height: 1;
    }
    .brand-text .bt-sub {
      font-size: 11.5px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-top: 3px;
    }
    .badge-live {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 7px;
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--brand-700);
      background: #e7faf2;
      border: 1px solid #c4efdd;
      padding: 6px 12px;
      border-radius: 999px;
    }
    .badge-live .dot {
      width: 7px; height: 7px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--brand);
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 rgba(52,204,153,.6);
      animation: pulse 1.8s ease-out infinite;
    }
    @keyframes pulse {
      0%   { box-shadow: 0 0 0 0   rgba(52,204,153,.55); }
      70%  { box-shadow: 0 0 0 8px rgba(52,204,153,0);   }
      100% { box-shadow: 0 0 0 0   rgba(52,204,153,0);   }
    }

    /* ============ HERO ============ */
    .hero {
      border-radius: var(--r-xl);
      overflow: hidden;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
      position: relative;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
      animation: heroIn .7s cubic-bezier(.22,.68,0,1.1) both;
    }
    .hero-bg {
      background:
        linear-gradient(165deg, #0f3827 0%, #082418 48%, #04130c 100%);
      padding: 40px 34px 34px;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    /* soft corner glow */
    .hero-bg::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      width: 420px; height: 420px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(52,204,153,.22) 0%, rgba(52,204,153,.08) 40%, transparent 70%);
      top: -180px; right: -120px;
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    /* faint grid */
    .hero-bg::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute; inset: 0;
      background-image:
        linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,.022) 1px, transparent 1px),
        linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,.022) 1px, transparent 1px);
      background-size: 34px 34px;
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    .hero-inner { position: relative; z-index: 2; }

    .eyebrow {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: .4px;
      color: var(--brand);
      background: rgba(52,204,153,.1);
      border: 1px solid rgba(52,204,153,.25);
      padding: 6px 12px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }
    .eyebrow i { font-size: 10px; }

    .hero-title {
      font-size: 32px;
      font-weight: 900;
      color: #fff;
      line-height: 1.25;
      letter-spacing: -.6px;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .hero-title .accent { color: var(--brand); }

    .hero-sub {
      font-size: 15.5px;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,.72);
      font-weight: 500;
      line-height: 1.65;
      margin-bottom: 26px;
      max-width: 56ch;
    }

    .hero-actions {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 10px;
      align-items: center;
    }
    .btn {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 9px;
      font-family: inherit;
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 800;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 13px 22px;
      cursor: pointer;
      border: 1px solid transparent;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: transform .15s ease, box-shadow .2s ease, background .2s ease;
    }
    .btn-primary {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--brand) 0%, var(--brand-600) 100%);
      color: #042a1d;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 24px rgba(52,204,153,.35), inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,.3);
    }
    .btn-primary:hover { transform: translateY(-1px); box-shadow: 0 14px 30px rgba(52,204,153,.45), inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,.35); }
    .btn-ghost {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.06);
      color: #fff;
      border-color: rgba(255,255,255,.14);
    }
    .btn-ghost:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,.1); }

    /* ============ STATS STRIP ============ */
    .hero-strip {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      background: rgba(3,12,8,.96);
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.06);
    }
    .hs-item {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 18px 12px;
      gap: 4px;
      border-left: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.05);
    }
    .hs-item:first-child { border-left: none; }
    .hs-val {
      font-size: 19px;
      font-weight: 900;
      color: #fff;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 6px;
    }
    .hs-val .star { color: var(--gold); font-size: 14px; }
    .hs-val .up   { color: var(--brand); font-size: 12px; }
    .hs-lbl {
      font-size: 11.5px;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,.5);
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    /* ============ MESSAGE CARD ============ */
    .message-card {
      background: var(--card);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--r-lg);
      padding: 22px 22px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 16px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
      position: relative;
    }
    .message-card::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 22px; bottom: 22px;
      right: 0;
      width: 3px;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--brand), var(--brand-700));
      border-radius: 3px 0 0 3px;
    }
    .mc-icon {
      width: 44px; height: 44px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      background: #eafaf3;
      color: var(--brand-700);
      display: grid; place-items: center;
      font-size: 18px;
      flex-shrink: 0;
      border: 1px solid #cdeddd;
    }
    .mc-body .mc-title {
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: var(--brand-ink);
      margin-bottom: 3px;
    }
    .mc-body .mc-text {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: var(--ink-2);
      line-height: 1.65;
    }

    /* ============ SECTION LABEL ============ */
    .section-label {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      margin: 26px 4px 14px;
    }
    .sl-title {
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: var(--muted);
      letter-spacing: .8px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }
    .sl-hint {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: var(--muted-2);
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    /* ============ FEATURES ============ */
    .feat-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .feat {
      background: var(--card);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--r-md);
      padding: 18px 18px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 14px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
      transition: transform .18s ease, box-shadow .18s ease, border-color .18s ease;
    }
    .feat:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
      border-color: var(--border-strong);
    }
    .feat-icon {
      width: 40px; height: 40px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      display: grid; place-items: center;
      font-size: 16px;
      flex-shrink: 0;
      background: #eafaf3;
      color: var(--brand-700);
      border: 1px solid #cdeddd;
    }
    .feat-icon.gold {
      background: var(--gold-soft);
      color: var(--gold);
      border-color: #f3e2b2;
    }
    .feat-body .ft {
      font-size: 14.5px;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: var(--brand-ink);
      margin-bottom: 2px;
    }
    .feat-body .fd {
      font-size: 12.5px;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.55;
    }

    /* ============ CTA FOOTER CARD ============ */
    .cta-card {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffffff 0%, #f2fbf6 100%);
      border: 1px solid var(--border-strong);
      border-radius: var(--r-lg);
      padding: 22px 24px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 18px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .cta-left .cta-title {
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 900;
      color: var(--brand-ink);
      margin-bottom: 2px;
    }
    .cta-left .cta-sub {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-weight: 500;
    }
    .cta-btn {
      background: var(--brand-ink);
      color: #fff;
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 12px 18px;
      font-weight: 800;
      font-size: 14px;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: background .2s ease, transform .15s ease;
    }
    .cta-btn:hover { background: #000; transform: translateY(-1px); }

    /* ============ FOOTER ============ */
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 12.5px;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-top: 28px;
      font-weight: 500;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }
    .footer .divider {
      width: 32px; height: 2px;
      background: var(--border-strong);
      margin: 0 auto 12px;
      border-radius: 2px;
    }
    .footer .partner {
      color: var(--ink-2);
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    /* ============ ANIMATIONS ============ */
    @keyframes heroIn {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(-14px) scale(.985); }
      to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0) scale(1); }
    }

    /* ============ RESPONSIVE ============ */
    @media (max-width: 520px) {
      .page { padding: 22px 16px 0; }
      .hero-bg { padding: 32px 22px 28px; }
      .hero-title { font-size: 26px; }
      .hero-sub { font-size: 14px; }
      .feat-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .btn { padding: 12px 18px; font-size: 14px; }
      .cta-card { flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; }
      .hs-val { font-size: 17px; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="page">

    <!-- Top bar -->
    

    <!-- Hero -->
    <div class="hero">
      <div class="hero-bg">
        <div class="hero-inner">
          <div class="eyebrow">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-bell"></i>
          </div>
          <h1 class="hero-title">
               <span class="accent">صباح الخير ☀️</span>
          </h1>
          <p class="hero-sub">
رحلتك المثالية تبدأ مع ناقل 
احجز الآن وانطلق براحة.</p>
          <div class="hero-actions">
            <a class="btn btn-primary" href="#">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-location-dot"></i>
              احجز رحلتك الآن
            </a>
           
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-strip">
        <div class="hs-item">
          <div class="hs-val">4.9 <i class="fa-solid fa-star star"></i></div>
          <div class="hs-lbl">تقييم اليوم</div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="hs-item">
          <div class="hs-val">24/7 <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-up up"></i></div>
          <div class="hs-lbl">خدمة متواصلة</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Message -->
    <div class="message-card">
      <div class="mc-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-route"></i></div>
      <div class="mc-body">
        <div class="mc-title">انطلق بثقة، وأكمل يومك بسلاسة</div>
        <div class="mc-text">
          فريق ناقل جاهز لخدمتك على مدار الساعة — بضغطة واحدة تصلك سيارة مريحة بسائق موثوق وسعر عادل.
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Section label -->
    <div class="section-label">
    </div>

    <!-- Features -->
    <div class="feat-grid">
      <div class="feat">
        <div class="feat-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-couch"></i></div>
        <div class="feat-body">
          <div class="ft">راحة تامة</div>
          <div class="fd">سيارات حديثة ومكيّفة لكل رحلة</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="feat">
        <div class="feat-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-shield-halved"></i></div>
        <div class="feat-body">
          <div class="ft">أمان كامل</div>
          <div class="fd">سائقون موثوقون ومرخّصون رسمياً</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="feat">
        <div class="feat-icon gold"><i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i></div>
        <div class="feat-body">
          <div class="ft">موثوقية عالية</div>
          <div class="fd">آلاف العملاء يثقون بناقل يومياً</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="feat">
        <div class="feat-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-sack-dollar"></i></div>
        <div class="feat-body">
          <div class="ft">أسعار عادلة</div>
          <div class="fd">أفضل التعرفات بجودة لا تُضاهى</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- CTA card -->
    <div class="cta-card">
      <div class="cta-left">
        <div class="cta-title">جاهز للانطلاق؟</div>
        <div class="cta-sub">احجز رحلتك خلال ثوانٍ عبر تطبيق ناقل.</div>
      </div>
      <a class="cta-btn" href="#">
        ابدأ الآن
        <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-left"></i>
      </a>
    </div>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <div class="footer">
      <div class="divider"></div>
      <div><span class="partner">ناقل</span> — بالشراكة مع وزارة النقل العراقية</div>
      <div>© 2026 جميع الحقوق محفوظة</div>
    </div>

  </div>
</body>
</html>
